Properties.Name: Days Without Giving
Properties.Description: How many days back has giving leader not given at all?

Properties.Value:
SELECT DV.Id as [Value], DV.Value as [Text]
FROM DefinedValue DV
WHERE DV.DefinedTypeId = 4
ORDER BY DV.Value
